Hobemian Records | website = [http://hobemianrecords.com/delrey.html hobemianrecords.com/delrey.html] | notable_instruments = [[Ron Phillips]] [[resonator guitar]] and [[ukulele]] }} '''Del Rey''' (born December 22, 1959, [[Los Angeles]], [[California]], [[United States]]) is an [[United States|American]] [[blues]], [[jazz]] and [[ragtime]] [[singer]] (and occasional songwriter), [[guitarist]] and [[ukulele]] player. ==Biography== Starting with [[classical music]] at the age of four, she was transfixed by her first blues album and has played blues and jazz ever since.
